    "notes": "Released in a outside laminated gatefold cover. Note, that the front and back of the sleeve are laminated, but the inside is not.\nThis LP has \"Pink Rim\" labels. \n\nThis first pressing has \"℗ 1970\" on center right of both labels.\n\nThere are also 2 nearly identical label variations:\n– \"℗ 1970 Island Records Ltd.\" [url=http://www.discogs.com/release/3846885]on label side A only[/url] and \"℗ 1970\" on label side B;\n– \"℗ 1970 Island Records Ltd.\" [url=http://www.discogs.com/release/5369065]credited on both sides of label[/url].\n\nAs printed on [url=https://www.discogs.com/release/1156598#images/30465769]the Side 2 vinyl label[/url], a duration for Track Bc is given (10:55), but there are no times listed for the sub-tracks within 'The Battle Of Glass Tears'.\n\nAll songs published by E.G. Music\n",
    "released_formatted": "11 Dec 1970",
